{
  "chapter": 27,
  "chapter_summary": "本章马如龙与张老实身陷被拆空的死地，外面黑衣壮汉不断运来珍贵黑石铺地，令张老实骤然恐惧。张老实取出碧玉珠救治铁震天，身份随即被马如龙逼问揭开，原来她就是碧玉山庄门下大婉。大婉说明自己曾在寒梅谷亲见诸多巧合，故意放走并多次试探马如龙，认定他并非凶手，却苦于邱凤城计划周密无证可举。她又解释制住谢玉宝是为拖延婚期、阻止其嫁给邱凤城。众人因朋友之义互相谅解，大婉承认此前绿色烟雾是碧玉山庄翠寒烟，但黑衣人与黑石出现后，她判断众人已难全身而退。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": "char_zhang_lao_shi",
      "text": "你看见了什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 12,
      "line_end": 12
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhang_lao_shi",
      "speaker_name": "张老实",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "我什么都没有看见。",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 14,
      "line_end": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": "char_zhang_lao_shi",
      "text": "就算他们要把我们困死在这里，也不必把屋子都拆光的，他们可以躲在屋子里，用这些屋子作掩护。",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 16,
      "line_end": 18
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhang_lao_shi",
      "speaker_name": "张老实",
      "listener": "char_tie_zhen_tian",
      "text": "这是给你的，你先吃一半，留一半，先嚼碎，再吞下去。",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 50,
      "line_end": 52
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_zhen_tian",
      "speaker_name": "铁震天",
      "listener": "char_zhang_lao_shi",
      "text": "这是什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 54,
      "line_end": 54
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhang_lao_shi",
      "speaker_name": "张老实",
      "listener": "char_tie_zhen_tian",
      "text": "这就是碧玉珠。半个时辰内，就可以把你的伤势治好一半，黄昏时你再服下另外一半，气力就可以恢复八成了。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 56,
      "line_end": 58
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhang_lao_shi",
      "speaker_name": "张老实",
      "listener": "char_tie_zhen_tian",
      "text": "只希望你能够活到那时候。",
      "tone": "担心",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 58,
      "line_end": 60
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_zhen_tian",
      "speaker_name": "铁震天",
      "listener": "char_zhang_lao_shi",
      "text": "你是谁？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 66,
      "line_end": 66
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_zhen_tian",
      "speaker_name": "铁震天",
      "listener": "char_zhang_lao_shi",
      "text": "你怎么会有碧玉珠？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 66,
      "line_end": 66
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhang_lao_shi",
      "speaker_name": "张老实",
      "listener": "char_tie_zhen_tian",
      "text": "这全都跟你没有关系。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 68,
      "line_end": 68
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_zhen_tian",
      "speaker_name": "铁震天",
      "listener": "char_zhang_lao_shi",
      "text": "有关系。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 70,
      "line_end": 70
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_zhen_tian",
      "speaker_name": "铁震天",
      "listener": "char_zhang_lao_shi",
      "text": "我铁震天这一生中，从未平白无故受人的好处，我若不知道你是谁，怎么能够拿你的药？",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 70,
      "line_end": 72
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": "char_tie_zhen_tian",
      "text": "你可以拿他的药，也可以接受他的恩惠，而且用不着报答他。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 74,
      "line_end": 76
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_zhen_tian",
      "speaker_name": "铁震天",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 78,
      "line_end": 78
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": "char_tie_zhen_tian",
      "text": "因为他是我的朋友，你也是的，朋友之间，无论谁为谁做了什么事，都不必提起'报答'二字。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 80,
      "line_end": 82
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_wan_wu",
      "speaker_name": "王万武",
      "listener": "char_tie_zhen_tian",
      "text": "铁震天，现在你不妨杀了我，我已死而无憾。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 86,
      "line_end": 88
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": "char_zhang_lao_shi",
      "text": "现在，你是不是已经应该承认了？",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 96,
      "line_end": 98
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhang_lao_shi",
      "speaker_name": "张老实",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "承认什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 100,
      "line_end": 100
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": "char_zhang_lao_shi",
      "text": "承认你就是大碗！",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 102,
      "line_end": 102
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhang_lao_shi",
      "speaker_name": "张老实",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "不错，我就是大婉。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 104,
      "line_end": 104
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhang_lao_shi",
      "speaker_name": "大婉",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "铁震天的气力已将恢复，王万武不该死，你也不必死。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 114,
      "line_end": 116
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhang_lao_shi",
      "speaker_name": "大婉",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "只要一有机会，你们就可以冲出去。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 118,
      "line_end": 118
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": "char_zhang_lao_shi",
      "text": "你呢？",
      "tone": "担心",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 120,
      "line_end": 120
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhang_lao_shi",
      "speaker_name": "大婉",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "我……",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 122,
      "line_end": 122
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_yu_bao",
      "speaker_name": "谢玉宝",
      "listener": "char_zhang_lao_shi",
      "text": "你们为什么不问问我？我应该怎么办？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 124,
      "line_end": 124
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_yu_bao",
      "speaker_name": "谢玉宝",
      "listener": "char_zhang_lao_shi",
      "text": "你为什么要把我害成这样子？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 128,
      "line_end": 128
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhang_lao_shi",
      "speaker_name": "大婉",
      "listener": "char_xie_yu_bao",
      "text": "我对不起你。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 130,
      "line_end": 130
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhang_lao_shi",
      "speaker_name": "大婉",
      "listener": "char_xie_yu_bao",
      "text": "但是你一定要相信我。我绝不是故意要害你。",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 130,
      "line_end": 132
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_yu_bao",
      "speaker_name": "谢玉宝",
      "listener": "char_zhang_lao_shi",
      "text": "你为什么要做这种事？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 134,
      "line_end": 134
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhang_lao_shi",
      "speaker_name": "大婉",
      "listener": "char_xie_yu_bao",
      "text": "因为我不能让你嫁给邱凤城。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 136,
      "line_end": 136
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhang_lao_shi",
      "speaker_name": "大婉",
      "listener": "char_xie_yu_bao",
      "text": "我们是从小就在一起长大的，我绝不能让你嫁给那种阴狠歹毒的人。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 138,
      "line_end": 140
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": "char_zhang_lao_shi",
      "text": "她就是碧玉夫人的女儿？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 142,
      "line_end": 142
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhang_lao_shi",
      "speaker_name": "大婉",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "她就是，谢夫人将你们召到寒梅谷去，就是为了替她找一个好丈夫。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 144,
      "line_end": 146
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": "char_zhang_lao_shi",
      "text": "那天你也去了？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 148,
      "line_end": 148
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhang_lao_shi",
      "speaker_name": "大婉",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "那天我不但去了，而且亲眼看到了所有的变化。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 150,
      "line_end": 150
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhang_lao_shi",
      "speaker_name": "大婉",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "但是我却认为那其中一定还另有机谋。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 154,
      "line_end": 154
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": "char_zhang_lao_shi",
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 156,
      "line_end": 156
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhang_lao_shi",
      "speaker_name": "大婉",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "因为其中的巧合太多了。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 158,
      "line_end": 158
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhang_lao_shi",
      "speaker_name": "大婉",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "我一直不相信巧合太多的事。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 158,
      "line_end": 160
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhang_lao_shi",
      "speaker_name": "大婉",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "谢夫人叫我到那里去，就是为了要我替她选择，这件事关系到大小姐的终生幸福。\n我绝不能轻易下判断。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 166,
      "line_end": 168
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhang_lao_shi",
      "speaker_name": "大婉",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "所以，我故意让你逃走，就因为我还要试探试探你，看你究竟是个什么样的人？",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 170,
      "line_end": 172
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhang_lao_shi",
      "speaker_name": "大婉",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "如果你没有停下来救我，那天你就已死在我手里。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 174,
      "line_end": 174
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhang_lao_shi",
      "speaker_name": "大婉",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "经过无数次试探后，我才相信你绝不是个阴险恶毒的人，我已经开始怀疑邱凤城。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 180,
      "line_end": 180
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhang_lao_shi",
      "speaker_name": "大婉",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "只可惜这计划实在太周密巧妙，连我都抓不到他的一点破绽。\n虽然我明知你是被冤枉的，也没法子替你洗刷。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 182,
      "line_end": 184
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhang_lao_shi",
      "speaker_name": "大婉",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "因为我完全没有证据，要让谢夫人相信你是无辜的，一定要有证据。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 184,
      "line_end": 186
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": "char_zhang_lao_shi",
      "text": "就算碧玉夫人肯相信，绝大师他们也不会放过我的。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 188,
      "line_end": 190
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhang_lao_shi",
      "speaker_name": "大婉",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "后来我才知道，就在我一直跟踪你的时候，谢夫人已经决定选邱凤城做女婿了，甚至连婚期都已决定。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 192,
      "line_end": 194
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_wan_wu",
      "speaker_name": "王万武",
      "listener": "char_zhang_lao_shi",
      "text": "这件事我好像也听说过。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 196,
      "line_end": 196
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhang_lao_shi",
      "speaker_name": "大婉",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "谢夫人已经决定了的事，一向很少更改。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 198,
      "line_end": 198
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhang_lao_shi",
      "speaker_name": "大婉",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "除非我能找到真凭实据，能证明这是邱凤城的阴谋。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 198,
      "line_end": 200
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhang_lao_shi",
      "speaker_name": "大婉",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "他这个计划不但周密巧妙，做得更绝，连我都不能不佩服他，但是要我眼看着他把大小姐娶回去，我也不甘心。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 208,
      "line_end": 210
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_yu_bao",
      "speaker_name": "谢玉宝",
      "listener": "char_zhang_lao_shi",
      "text": "这时候我已经出来了，并不是出来看邱凤城的，是出来找你的。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 212,
      "line_end": 214
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhang_lao_shi",
      "speaker_name": "大婉",
      "listener": "char_xie_yu_bao",
      "text": "我明白，不管你嘴里怎么说，你心里一直都把我看作你的姐妹。",
      "tone": "柔声",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 216,
      "line_end": 218
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_yu_bao",
      "speaker_name": "谢玉宝",
      "listener": "char_zhang_lao_shi",
      "text": "可是我连做梦都没有想到，你会忽然出手制住我。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 220,
      "line_end": 220
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhang_lao_shi",
      "speaker_name": "大婉",
      "listener": "char_xie_yu_bao",
      "text": "我只有那么做。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 222,
      "line_end": 222
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhang_lao_shi",
      "speaker_name": "大婉",
      "listener": "char_xie_yu_bao",
      "text": "我想来想去，最好的法子，就是先把你们两个人藏起来，让别人找不到你们，也让你能渐渐了解马如龙是个什么样的人。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 228,
      "line_end": 230
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhang_lao_shi",
      "speaker_name": "大婉",
      "listener": "char_xie_yu_bao",
      "text": "故意先让他知道你是个美丽的女孩子，也是为了要试探他，在暗室之中，是不是还能把握住自己。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 230,
      "line_end": 232
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_yu_bao",
      "speaker_name": "谢玉宝",
      "listener": "char_zhang_lao_shi",
      "text": "所以你也来陪着我们，因为你还是不太放心。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 234,
      "line_end": 234
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhang_lao_shi",
      "speaker_name": "大婉",
      "listener": "char_xie_yu_bao",
      "text": "如果他敢对你怎么样，我也不会让他活到现在的。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 236,
      "line_end": 236
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_yu_bao",
      "speaker_name": "谢玉宝",
      "listener": "char_zhang_lao_shi",
