    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_zhen_tian",
      "speaker_name": "铁震天",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "他本来就是个好人，这件事，本来也是件好事，只可惜，他这个好人却偏偏交了个坏朋友。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 244,
      "line_end": 246
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": "char_tie_zhen_tian",
      "text": "朋友就是朋友，朋友绝不分好坏，因为朋友只有一种，如果你对不起我，出卖了我，你根本就不是我的朋友，根本就不配说这两个字。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 248,
      "line_end": 248
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": "char_tie_zhen_tian",
      "text": "我不信神，不信佛，我只相信朋友。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 250,
      "line_end": 252
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_zhen_tian",
      "speaker_name": "铁震天",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "我明白你的意思，",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 254,
      "line_end": 254
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_zhen_tian",
      "speaker_name": "铁震天",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "但是，你若没有我这个朋友，你的身份就不会暴露，不管怎么样，总是我连累了你。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 254,
      "line_end": 256
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": "char_tie_zhen_tian",
      "text": "你是不是后悔交了我这个朋友，还是要让我后悔交了你这个朋友？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 258,
      "line_end": 260
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_zhen_tian",
      "speaker_name": "铁震天",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "我不后悔，",
