      "speaker": "char_tie_zhen_tian",
      "speaker_name": "铁震天",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "我知道你也绝不会后悔的。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 262,
      "line_end": 262
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_wan_wu",
      "speaker_name": "王万武",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "看见你们这样的朋友，我才知道我这一辈子从来都没有交到朋友。",
